title: SketchList3D
description: SketchList is a woodworking design software built by woodworkers. That means it uses woodworking terms and practices so that woodworkers can focus on their craft. Its user-friendly 3D modeling features allow you to build life-like visualizations of your products, ensuring that they are accurate and ready to be built to perfection. With SketchList 3D, you can avoid the headache of traditional CAD software and design projects with more confidence.
